Probably my favorite Subway so far. That means I will be super biased and ramble on how good this one is.  There actually isn't much to say. I've been here several times, and sandwiches are consistently fine. Basically you get a sandwich you expect from Subway. The wait for the order is acceptable.  There are good amount of seats. The employees are okay.  There is a fairly clean washroom.  What more do you want from a Subway franchise?

This is your standard Subway restaurant. The food is good and tasty, but the employees working here make it spectular. They are patient and will work with you to make the meal you want to eat. They are more than willing to take special orders, adjust how they cut the sandwich, and just be considerate of allergies and preferences.  This is my favorite subway to go to.
